      • getRegradeOption

        public String getRegradeOption()
        Denotes if regrading is available for the question. Possible values are 'available' and 'unavailable' for question types 'multiple_answers_question', 'multiple_choice_question', 'true_false_question' and 'NULL' for others. Defaults to 'available' for the allowed question types and 'NULL' for the rest.
